Ques 02 — Employee Project Allocation System.

Project Overview
----------------

Create a Spring Core application to assign projects to employees using setter injection.

Classes
--------
Project: projectId, projectName
Employee: empId, name, project (dependency)

System Description
------------------
Project details are injected into employee objects dynamically using setter injection configured in XML.

Real-Time Scenario
-------------------
Used in IT companies to allocate projects to employees.

Expected Output
----------------
Display employee and project details
